# Screen sharing app

Stream your desktop with a simple python script through a web interface.
Through this web interface you can control the mouse.
Based on: (github link ?)


# Requirements

This app required the following package:
 * gtk
 * open-cv2
 * numpy (> 1.11.3)
 * Image

# Run

To run this app you need to use WSGI HTTP Server. I used gunicorn:
```
 gunicorn -w 4 main:app -b 0.0.0.0:4000
```
And connect go to
```
http://0.0.0.0:5000
```
